{"tid":949004,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"兒童睇得多動畫會對心智做成不良影響","createTime":"2018-12-20T13:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T01:20:40.000Z","uid":8307,"like":15,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"03948aab7e1b0872be13c4bb5badc7f44fcb4e2f","tid":949004,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"做緊個project，研究緊呢樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n普遍係一堆 將事情或角色非黑即白 嘅動畫<br />\n<br />\n節目將角色分正派反派，好嘅就一定正義，壞嘅就衰到仆街，漸漸就養成睇電視一開場就估條友係忠定奸<br />\n<br />\n師奶都會不過唔係研究對象啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n非黑即白，現實好容易隨便將人分成好人同壞人，對自己唔太禮貌嘅都變成壞人 衰人 反派 ，往往待人接物、朋輩間嘅磨合輸一大截<br />\n<br />\n暫時post呢啲部分內容<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"3c879d9a8a201f861941f797856bf992c895c42a","tid":949004,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:30:26.000Z","msg":"我係唔係勾返起其他人以前被校園欺凌嘅回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a40f99b49387cfacd50b9c428ddfe0c137afbd4","tid":949004,"uid":201823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8202f2b7a8fbefe4fb00bd4d8d0b6caf24beef13","tid":949004,"uid":14719,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"樓主細個俾人研究過"},{"pid":"42cb4fa6ef95c1833a26cc640edc091fefc3f9b0","tid":949004,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"試下睇魔禁"},{"pid":"5ad7efba8022727816acc34b25e8c42ae77ebe0a","tid":949004,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a40f99b49387cfacd50b9c428ddfe0c137afbd4","tid":949004,"uid":201823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:37:45.000Z","msg":"基連唔係反派<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b6d0f4120d2cfbb929c96500f7b71b